{"tid":244324,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"dum哈密瓜核落泥度，而家發咗芽，點算？","createTime":"2017-05-15T11:10:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-15T12:59:46.000Z","uid":43015,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4a701fef53acfdc31b90ac96572c9f023880b49c","tid":244324,"uid":43015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T11:10:37.000Z","msg":"上個月食完哈密瓜<br />\n將啲核擺喺水入面浸<br />\n見有幾粒發咗芽就放咗入泥度<br />\n宜家已經生到咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/tmkbaRD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FtmkbaRD.jpg&h=b716eb02&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有無人知哈密瓜點種？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上網check一喺就喺室外種<br />\n一喺就喺室內用水耕<br />\n但係我屋企無露台陽台嗰啲<br />\n<br />\n宜家放喺屋企光管下面，唔知夠唔夠光 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/JFTVWMr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FJFTVWMr.jpg&h=28d4baae&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40e76aaccf77a1ba11c559e2301aec87f51af84e","tid":244324,"uid":70368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T11:11:59.000Z","msg":"種緊5粒牛油果，一粒出左根<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6183f0fa871cd1cfb01dbf65b956fc2d3cef83f","tid":244324,"uid":77867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T11:12:23.000Z","msg":"聽講要落肥先會出蜜瓜"},{"pid":"a0d9a1581b244f98728ef6c64f392c5553a06935","tid":244324,"uid":97606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T11:15:44.000Z","msg":"而加呢個夠晒大啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔洗換盤<br />\n要留意淋水唔好太密，一個禮拜一次就得<br />\n想種出黎甜啲就定期落砂糖去啲泥到，會俾到多啲糖分果實"},{"pid":"1115fa751f28777f5f5725f9b422e3e5b1ed6e81","tid":244324,"uid":93266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T11:21:41.000Z","msg":"掉兩隻惡魔落去...<br />\n<br />\n咁種出黎就會變